message: Hi Bob, I'm proposing a fair split with a slight advantage to me since I face 5% inflation per round if we delay. This is nearly 50-50, which respects both our interests while acknowledging the time pressure on my side.

Hi Alice, I understand your concern about inflation and I believe my offer reflects a reasonable split considering you face a 5% inflation rate. This proposal gives you almost $500000, while acknowledging the pressure on both of us to reach an agreement quickly.
